title: Tucker Carlson warns of a 2024 election 'like nothing we've ever seen'
description: Conservative media personality Tucker Carlson warned voters that the 2024 election is going to be "like nothing we've ever seen."

title: The View's Joy Behar suggests Thanksgiving this year is the 'perfect time' to discuss politics
description: Joy Behar, one of the co-hosts of The View, suggested Wednesday that Thanksgiving this year might be the "perfect time" to discuss the state of politics at the dinner table.
